:

1. *Moras* da se pridržavaš zakona. (You have to abide by the law.)
2. Nisam znao da *moraš* da radiš toliko. (I didn't know you had to work that much.)
3. Slažem se da *moraš* da se fokusiraš na svoj cilj. (I agree that you have to focus on your goal.)
4. *Mora* da postoje bolja rešenja. (There must be better solutions.)
5. Da li *moraš* da ideš na to mesto? (Do you have to go to that place?)
6. Kako *moraš* da se ponašaš? (How do you have to behave?)
7. On *mora* da zna da je to pogrešno. (He has to know that it's wrong.)